text: Lule책 BBK is a basketball club in the town of Lule책 in Sweden. The club was established in 1978. Before the 2011-2012 season the club changed its names to Northland Basket. The club changed back to its original name in mid-July 2015. The club won the Swedish women's national basketball championship in 2014, 2015, 2016 and 2017.
